comment: * VideoTranscodingRequest encapsulates the configuration for transcoding a video.

variables.name: mVideoTrackFormat
variables.comment:
* Desired output video format of the destination file. *

If this is null, source file's video track will be passed through and copied to the * destination file.

variables.name: mAudioTrackFormat
variables.comment:
* Desired output audio format of the destination file. *

If this is null, source file's audio track will be passed through and copied to the * destination file.

methods.name: public MediaFormat getVideoTrackFormat()
methods.comment:
* Return the video track format of the transcoding.
         * This will be null if client has not specified the video track format.
